#\#CIF_2.0
# Tests: schema-less ingestion of multiple data blocks. Each block's tags must
# appear in _cif_fallback with the correct _block_id. Tags in block_alpha must
# not bleed into block_beta rows and vice versa. All block IDs must be present
# in the distinct _block_id values of _cif_fallback.
# Identical content in different blocks must not collide.
# Dictionary: none (schema-less)

data_block_alpha
_sample.name  alpha_sample
_sample.color red
_value.a      1.0

data_block_beta
_sample.name  beta_sample
_sample.color blue
_value.b      2.0
_value.c      3.0

data_block_gamma
_sample.name  beta_sample
_sample.color blue
_value.b      2.0
_value.c      3.0